    <!-- Info window -->
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_Title">About ClickyKeys</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_Tagline">Key &amp; click counter for gamers and geeks</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_Features">Features</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_Feature1">• Counts key presses and mouse clicks you care about.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_Feature2">• Lets you assign custom labels to keys (e.g. Jump, Reload, Ability 1).</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_Feature3">• Fully customizable overlay: layout, button size, colors, font.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_Privacy">Privacy &amp; Source Available</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_PrivacyText1">ClickyKeys processes your key presses and mouse clicks locally — that data never leaves your PC. Separately, you can opt in to one of two anonymous usage-statistics tiers (Basic: identity only, or Full: identity plus how features are configured and used) to help us improve the app; this is off by default and can be changed any time in Settings → Data Collection.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_PrivacyText2">The project's source is available, so you can review the code, learn from it, or contribute improvements.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_Credits">Credits &amp; Thanks</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_CreditsText1">ClickyKeys is a hobby project that grows thanks to people who simply enjoy clicking with it.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Info_CreditsText2">Thanks for using ClickyKeys!</sys:String>
